## Limitations

This report is based on publicly available information and may not capture all nuances of tax avoidance strategies due to the complexity and evolving nature of tax laws. Additionally, the data is limited to sources available up to October 2023, and newer developments may not be reflected. The analysis is also constrained by the availability of detailed financial data on individual tax strategies, which is often proprietary or confidential.

